class: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Contract\\Hook\\CancellationTokenInterface"
type: interface
summary: Defines the contract for a cancellation token used to signal intent to abort long-running or asynchronous hook operations. It provides a mechanism for cooperative cancellation without requiring external state management.
